  "title": "Part Time Delivery Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Part Time Delivery Driver (Class 3 / 4)</strong><br /></p><p><strong>3 days work week ( either Mon/ Wed/ Fri or Tues/ Thurs/ Sat)</strong><br /></p><p>Job Description:<br /><br />· Assist in loading and unloading</p><p>· Ensure safe and timely delivery of items</p><p>· Collection of receipts and payments if any</p><p>· Meeting delivery deadline</p><p>· Others duties as per assigned by Supervisor<br /></p><p>Requirements:<br /></p><p>* Min 1-2 years of working experience</p><p>* Good communication, independent, committed, full of initiative</p><p>* Possess driving license (3 or 4 manual)</p><p>* Must be Physically fit<br /></p><p>Interested candidate may send in their resume either via email to: hr@puricare.com.sg or Whatsapp to: 96518935</p>",
